attributes.Long form description: The student opens the boxes and pulls the wheels out, assembling them with the wheel unit and locking them. The student pulls out the base and mounts the m6 head on it, putting the batteries in the device. The student counts all the camera lenses and removes all the lens hoods, cleaning the lens. The student turns on the M6 machine and drives it, then turns it off.
